4. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper's modeling of the cloud computing service as a queuing system can be seen as a control problem, and the analysis of user equilibrium behavior can be seen as a systems problem. 
5. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) - While not directly related to the paper's content, the use of queuing theory and auction theory may involve computational complexity considerations, making this category a possible fit.
